                      "name": "secP1",
                      "fill": "#A1A1AA",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Tuff is a Raycast-style desktop launcher built with Electron and Vue 3. It provides a unified command palette (CoreBox) that lets you search apps, run scripts, manage clipboard, trigger AI actions, and much more — all from a single keyboard shortcut.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "249OI",
                      "name": "secP2",
                      "fill": "#A1A1AA",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "The plugin architecture follows a three-layer design: Manifest for declarations, Prelude for lightweight scripts, and Surface for rich UI views.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
