                  "fill": "$gray-500",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "We use pay-as-you-go metering with hard budget caps. Admins can set monthly spend limits and receive threshold alerts before extra charges occur.",
